{"title":"广西民歌","authors":[],"dates":[{"year":1959,"month":12,"day":25}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"广西民歌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"丰收谣"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"总路线好像红太阳，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"照得山区变了样；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"缺粮县变成余粮县，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"喜讯报到怀仁堂。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（三江侗族）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"七一公社一岁了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"七一公社诞生后，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好比一坡灵芝草，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"党的政策如春雨，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"灵芝日长五尺高。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"七一公社一岁了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好比泰山立城郊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"满山灵芝满山果，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"百鸟欢唱丰收谣。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（黄代荣）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"注：七一公社在全州城郊"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"青山腰间冒白烟"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"青山腰间冒白烟，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"白烟冲过山那边，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"牧童见了哈哈笑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他说这是云上天。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"弟弟弟弟别乱说，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这是工厂烧矿烟。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（南丹李友湘）"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":2,"page_end":2}